msgid "*Participant*: a country, economy or organization that joins GBIF by signing a https://www.gbif.org/document/80661[Memorandum of Understanding] and establishing a co-ordinated effort to support open access and use of biodiversity data, to advance scientific research, and to promote technological and sustainable development. Participant node: a coordinating team designated by the Participant to establish, strengthen and expand the collective GBIF activities in the country or organization.\n"
