#: 6.-what-is-the-recommended-process-for-establishing-a-participant-node/6.1-how-should-a-gbif-participant-select-the-institutional-location-for-a-node/README.en.adoc:49 6.-what-is-the-recommended-process-for-establishing-a-participant-node/6.1-how-should-a-gbif-participant-select-the-institutional-location-for-a-node/README.en.adoc:82
msgid "|High potential for developing capacity in biodiversity informatics easily and quickly"
msgstr "|Tienen mucho potencial para desarrollar fácil y rápidamente capacidades en informática de la biodiversidad"

