#: 6.-what-is-the-recommended-process-for-establishing-a-participant-node/6.1-how-should-a-gbif-participant-select-the-institutional-location-for-a-node/README.en.adoc:51
msgid "Full knowledge of the biodiversity-research realm"
msgstr "Gozan de pleno conocimiento del ámbito de la investigación sobre biodiversidad"

#. type: Plain text
#: 6.-what-is-the-recommended-process-for-establishing-a-participant-node/6.1-how-should-a-gbif-participant-select-the-institutional-location-for-a-node/README.en.adoc:53
msgid "May have a strong and clear institutional mandate"
